data.name: updates_info.Text
data.value:
STABLE is main updates channel. DEV has newer, but untested builds- they may not work properly or even not work at all!
If you don't know which to use, select STABLE.

data.name: Supporter_Instructions_Label.Text
data.value: To get supporter code donate $2 or more. Supporter code is for a lifetime. You will get your supporter code on your PayPal email. It may take up to 24h (probably less, may be even instant). If you didn't get your code, mail me at sean@seanasaservice.com. Please, do not share it (publicly shared codes may get banned).

data.name: MaxSpawnedAnimals_GroupBox.ToolTip
data.value:
If your server has a large number of players you can increase this limit to add more wildlife.
Animals don't consume as much CPU as zombies.
NOTE: That this doesn't cause more animals to spawn arbitrarily: The biome spawning system only spawns a certain number of animals in a given area, but if you have lots of players that are all spread out then you may be hitting the limit and can increase it.

data.name: www_main_content.Text
data.value:
Welcome to {server_name}!
To play please join IP: {server_ip}:{server_port}

This is sample website. You can use HTML tags here.



For example, you can put some screenshots here:


Note, that 7DSM WebServer doesn't support own images hosting yet, so you need to put them somewhere else, eg. imgur
Also please note that current implementation may be very CPU hungry. Avoid using it on big servers.

data.name: rules_content.Text
data.value:
Rules of {server_name}

1. Admin is always right
2. User can be banned for:
   -cheating
   -swearing
   -supporting The Borg


This is just example. Put your own rules here.
